OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMore people injecting drugs
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fworldwide, says UN         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, More people are injecting illegal drugs
OL,6, than previously thought, says a United 
OL,7, Nations report on worldwide drug use.  
OL,9,FIn all, 13.2 million people injected   
OL,10,Fdrugs in 2021, 18% more than previously
OL,11,Festimated, said the Vienna-based UN    
OL,12,FOffice on Drugs and Crime (UNODC).     
OL,14,FSynthetic substances such as fentanyl  
OL,15,Fand methamphetamine now dominate the   
OL,16,Fillegal drug markets, the UN says.     
OL,18,FGlobally, drug users increased by 23%  
OL,19,Fand drug-related disorders were up by  
OL,20,F45% in a decade to nearly 40 million.  
